Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.99,0:00:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.95,0:00:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.99,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使受了伤也无妨  不转移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想热切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.99,0:00:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我永不放弃的坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想紧紧抱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.99,0:01:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引导至鲜明的、一瞬间的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.99,0:01:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.31,0:01:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，这里是战士的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为那么单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个战场才会美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用令我们的故乡给战火蹂躏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这里作为人类最后的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.66,0:01:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只写在历史里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要长久地给世人流传才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许多战士会流干他们可贵的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有MD部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和敌人主力及游击部队交战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗只不过是开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙居民的决心有多坚定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十七话\N[激战的宇宙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,系统检查了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.57,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我留在这里直至战斗分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的特列斯难以击沉天秤座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.91,0:02:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时，我就破坏这艘舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要制止这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.42,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了和平须要流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是独裁者的理论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.12,0:02:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，正在战斗的那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了流血的心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我无意制止这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.07,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我一起留在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要保护我吗? 希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想在和杰克斯战斗时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要觉得亏欠他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这艘舰沉没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和王兄战斗的理由就会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战况看来势均力敌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，帮哪一边呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来势均力敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全因天秤座的主炮毫无动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为好像发一炮就会故障啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，全靠那样才有转机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但修理好后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙就会变得压倒性有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙只是代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙卫星的部份意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是整体意思的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星里众多的人应该渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，协助特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是对宇宙有益的行动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是天秤座和MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.54,0:04:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在成为威胁的是天秤座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧那看来的确是多余的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是希洛和莉莉娜小姐怎办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙自会想办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，决定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请把万年和平号\N就此驶向天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现万年和平号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它绕过战斗空域，驶向来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹还当我们是敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然呢，因为对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切力量都是敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不值一笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不派前线的MD去截击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法应付啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要动用三部比尔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有三部?怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那足以保住性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮还未修理好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你保护万年和平号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯的机体性能有差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来截击的对手恐怕是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他!只有三部比尔哥护卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,易如反掌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD也要看运用的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和木偶战斗真没趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹们和次代开始战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹们也非常讨厌杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我想多谢他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们并非为了我在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，蕾蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在的目的一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何要击沉天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们为何只是攻击卡特尔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道他想减少数目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他以为我是最易打倒的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想首先收拾指挥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么!我奉陪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧!五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你们组成队型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把MD布在有利的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的游击队也不能接近天秤座吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这情况，资源卫星MO-II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没动静吗?  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它只是在收容受损的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为他们准备了新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到只是一个补给基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!开动天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说要扰乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.31,0:08:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么美丽地战斗的双方阵型吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特司令也没奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.45,0:08:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯的骑士道精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,计算出绕过MO_II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达地球的路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也别忘记向司令报告啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那决定的确正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那能同时告诉宇宙的居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争是可悲的吗?米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在这样就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.28,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在一定要告诉\N地球宇宙的悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座离开战线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它看来正驶向MO_II啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的MO_II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几乎没留下兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦不能凭自力移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座大概打算绕过MO_II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驶向地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这艘舰追上去吧\N即使那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也没有击沉天秤座的武器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘舰有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只令天秤座主炮失效的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!难道…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫非战斗员离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MO_II会收容他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我们去副舰桥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是理所当然的行动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我现在不可让\N天秤座被击沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们向万年和平号…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒的攻击为何会被档开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那三部机合力在一处地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,张开强力的防护罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只好接近它们逐个击破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵! 让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.91,0:10:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，我不想和你战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵! 让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使要我打倒你也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么? 攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为何这么天真?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万年和平号一直冲过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.78,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能避开吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行! 赶不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开所有炮门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何要击沉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的撞过去就行吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了令那主炮失效呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺道也开动紧急推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎坏掉也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂! 怎样都好，那太鲁莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，只有那办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对那股勇气表示敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.42,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行! 要撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关掉引擎\N全体准备抵受撞击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伏在地上抱着头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万年和平号会撞过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一第三引擎严重受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省了关掉引擎的工夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去! 给我撞过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待会才报告损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点扑灭燃料库四周的火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.12,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮区域…彻底…被毁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于还未补充能量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮区域没有爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎会这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座…完了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗并未结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在击毁所有MD之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗会继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全军别松懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你保护了我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛! 你受了伤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样，杰克斯渴望的胜利幻灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄渴望的胜利?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,须要出动零式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报告损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮彻底不能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有若干损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能以70%马力移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那还有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也撞得很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是破坏天秤座变得很困难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是万年和平号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然暂时没有诱爆的危险性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们已经不能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我们从内部镇压天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破坏MD的控制系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求白色獠牙投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要救出希洛和莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破坏活动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我想起从前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后的拜托你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂! 五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他去，他看来早有约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们快点潜入天秤座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.71,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…但是…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你去吧，诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹入侵第17号闸门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是钢弹就没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让入侵的驾驶员深入舰内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹支援我们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型的钢弹05吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员是那个少年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，这场战争结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我弄清楚你的正义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到万年和平号后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就照霍华的指示离开这空域吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和哥哥再谈一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯决心坚定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.42,0:18:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是有人被囚禁的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，会有危险\N尽量远离房门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.38,0:18:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里的是希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.69,0:18:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂! 我究竟找到什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂! 找到了，在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝‧卡塔罗尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，卡特尔‧拉巴伯‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.92,0:19:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换言之杰克斯想给予地球打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想藉着行使绝大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唤醒人们心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.33,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对战争的恐惧及对和平的渴望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那样\N我们协助建造天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次开发拜叶特和麦丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你们我遇上不得了的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在天秤座的主炮里做了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不能连续发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全因设计上故意的错误啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说那是你们的赎罪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赎罪现在才开始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的不该找到他们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，和MO_II谈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体准备撤离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍华，希洛说出动飞翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他何时回来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
